'''杰夫·愛德華茲'''（{{lang-en|Geoffrey Bruce Owen "Geoff" Edwards}}，{{bd|1931年|2月15日|2014年|3月4日|catIdx=Edwards}}），是一名美国电影演员、游戏主持人、广播人物<ref name="la times">{{cite web|last=Chawkins|first=Steve|title=Geoff Edwards dies at 83; L.A. radio and TV personality|url=http://www.latimes.com/obituaries/la-me-geoff-edwards-20140306,0,3793049.story#axzz2vBnPQaIQ|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=6 March 2014|quote=Born Feb. 15, 1931, in Westfield, N.J., Geoffrey Bruce Owen Edwards...|archive-date=2014-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313015232/http://www.latimes.com/obituaries/la-me-geoff-edwards-20140306,0,3793049.story#axzz2vBnPQaIQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

早年在加利福尼亚州工作，后加入[[NBC|NBC]]、[[KMPC|KMPC]]。1973年开始加入美国广播公司的游戏节目。2014年3月5日，因肺炎并发症去世，享年83岁<ref>{{cite news |first=Mike |last=Barnes |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |title=Game Show Host Geoff Edwards Dies at 83 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/geoff-edwards-dies-veteran-game-686381 |date=March 5, 2014 |accessdate=March 6, 2014 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025061059/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/geoff-edwards-dies-veteran-game-686381 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Lynn |last=Elber |newspaper=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]] |title=Agent: Game show host Geoff Edwards dies at 83 |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_25283819/agent-game-show-host-geoff-edwards-dies-at |date=March 5, 2014 |accessdate=March 6, 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233151/http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_25283819/agent-game-show-host-geoff-edwards-dies-at |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

